title: Persilleriet
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Take-out, European, Norweigean
description: Each day 2 dishes at lunch and the Norwegian kind of early dinner ("middag"), plus three wraps called "kubbe" of which 2 are vegan. You could eat there or take away, which is slightly cheaper. Cozy place, seats 12. Staff knows which food is vegan suitable.
